import React from "react";
import { Card, Col, Container, Form, Row, Button } from "react-bootstrap";

const FormChoferes = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Container>
        <Card style={{ maxWidth: "100%" }}>
          <Card.Header>
            <Card.Title>Este es el title del formulario</Card.Title>
          </Card.Header>
          <Card.Body>
            <Form>
              <Row>
                <Col className="pr-1 col-md-8" >
                  <Form.Group>
                    <label htmlFor="nombre del Chofer">EMPRESA</label>
                    <Form.Control
                      defaultValue="Lexys Manuel."
                      placeholder="Nombre del Chofer."
                      type="text"
                    ></Form.Control>
                  </Form.Group>
                </Col>
              </Row>
              <Row>
                <Col className="px-1" md="3">
                  <Form.Group>
                    <label>Username</label>
                    <Form.Control
                      defaultValue="michael23"
                      placeholder="Username"
                      type="text"
                    ></Form.Control>
                  </Form.Group>
                </Col>
                <Col className="pl-1" md="4">
                  <Form.Group>
                    <label htmlFor="exampleInputEmail1">Email address</label>
                    <Form.Control
                      placeholder="Email"
                      type="email"
                    ></Form.Control>
                  </Form.Group>
                </Col>
              </Row>
              <Button
                className="btn-fill pull-right"
                type="submit"
                variant="info"
              >
                Update Profile
              </Button>
            </Form>
          </Card.Body>
        </Card>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
};

export default FormChoferes;
